{"tid":1561394,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"此風不可長","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:45:52.000Z","uid":263344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d11943251ca2927eab6d4184b5cd419a84c0f737","tid":1561394,"uid":263344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/54005/zip-bomb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F54005%2Fzip-bomb&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=287bdaaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/54005/zip-bomb</a><br />\n<br />\nzip且可追溯到幾十年前的5.25和3.5英吋軟碟時代。然而該技術作為一把雙面刃，也難免被別有用心的人所利用。比如透過一個看似超小型的壓縮包，製作一個內含巨量垃圾資料的「解壓炸彈包」（zip bomb）&mdash;&mdash;一個表面上只有46MB，但其實解壓縮後，可以膨脹到4.5PB的zbxl.zip炸彈壓縮包。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實早在去年，研究員大衛&middot;菲爾（David Fifield）就曾展示過早期的解壓炸彈包，能夠將一個42kB的zbsm.zip文件迅速膨脹到5.5GB。"},{"pid":"8471479a1bca79257fb1152e9335b1d8d99f748f","tid":1561394,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https